Class QualityRequirement

  • java.lang.Object
    • xml.QualityRequirement
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IQualityRequirement

    public class QualityRequirement
extends java.lang.Object
implements IQualityRequirement
    Class to hold the QualityRequirement of the requirement analysis. This class provides JAXB support and can be accessed via the IQualityRequirement Interface. Getter and Setter must be provided to be JAXB conform. It is implemented in the CustomXMLFormat.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    3852430
    See Also:
    IQualityRequirement, CustomXMLFormat
